**** sociolinguistics -- Frake and Ferguson
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ UP: <soclng00>
Other important methodological contributors to pidgin and creole sociolinguistic theory are Charles Frake, Charles Ferguson and Erving Goffman.


